public class AVLDictionary<K extends Comparable<K>, D> extends AVLTree<K,D> implements Dictionary<K,D>
Implementation of the Dictionary data structure with underlying AVL Tree representation.

  • Method Details

    • insert

      public void insert(K key, D data) throws IllegalStateException
      Inserts the mapping (key,data) into the dictionary; Cost: O(logn)

      Duplicated keys are not allowed: if key is already in the dictionary, the associated data is overwritten. Null key values are not allowed, while null data values are allowed.

      Specified by:

      public D delete(K key)
      Removes the mapping (key,data) from the dictionary and returns the data; Cost: Θ(logn)

      No action performed if the key is not in the dictionary
